  {
    question: "Can you clean before or after events at my Crestline home?",
    answer: "Absolutely. Crestline residents frequently host garden club gatherings, dinner parties, holiday celebrations, and charity events. We specialize in pre-event deep cleaning to ensure your home is flawless for guests and post-event restoration to return it to pristine condition. We offer flexible scheduling around your event timeline, including same-day and next-day service for last-minute occasions."
